<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="490" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,222,463]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1059,258,283]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
Moderate economic importance damage on 
<taxonomicName box="[280,345,295,318]" class="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" family="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" genus="Pyrus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[280,345,295,318]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Pyrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. (
<bibRefCitation box="[398,539,294,319]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" refId="ref21632" refString="Rajabi, Gh. (1991) Insects attacking Rosaceous fruit trees in Iran. Vol. 3: Homoptera. Ministry of Agriculture, Tehran, 256 pp." type="book">Rajabi 1991</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[551,678,294,319]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" refId="ref17343" refString="Abaii, M. (2000) Pests of Forest Trees and Shrubs of Iran. 2 nd Edition. Ministry of Agriculture, Agricultural Research, Education &amp; Extension Organization, Tehran, 178 pp." type="book">Abaii 2000</bibRefCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,222,463]" box="[199,1096,330,355]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,934,330,355]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,222,463]" box="[199,1150,366,391]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,562,366,391]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Recorded distribution in Iran:</emphasis>
North and southwest (
<bibRefCitation box="[815,1139,366,391]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" refId="ref20841" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2016) A checklist of the leafhoppers of Iran (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Zootaxa, 4062 (1), 1 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4062.1.1" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,222,463]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,402,427]" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Conclusion:</emphasis>
Its pest status in Iran needs further confirmation. It was previously recorded under the name 
<taxonomicName authority="Dlabola" authorityName="Dlabola" authorityYear="1974" box="[151,475,438,463]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Stegelytra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sororcula">
<emphasis box="[151,377,438,463]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">Stegelytra sororcula</emphasis>
Dlabola
</taxonomicName>
, a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Ghauri" baseAuthorityYear="1972" box="[720,888,439,462]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Stegelytra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="neveosparsa">
<emphasis box="[720,888,439,462]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="490">S. neveosparsa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
